functionDecorators.name: feeReceiver
functionDecorators.description: the address who receives auction fees.

functionDecorators.name: maxMaxAuctionLength
functionDecorators.description: the longest an auction can ever be.

functionDecorators.name: maxReserveFactor
functionDecorators.description: the max % increase over the initial.

functionDecorators.name: minBidIncrease
functionDecorators.description: the % bid increase required for a new bid.

functionDecorators.name: minMinAuctionLength
functionDecorators.description: the shortest an auction can ever be.

functionDecorators.name: minReserveFactor
functionDecorators.description: the max % decrease from the initial.

functionDecorators.name: minVotePercentage
functionDecorators.description: the % of tokens required to be voting for an auction to start.

functionDecorators.name: owner
functionDecorators.description: Returns the address of the current owner.

functionDecorators.name: renounceOwnership
functionDecorators.description: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

functionDecorators.name: transferOwnership
functionDecorators.description: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.
